    "0": {
      "uid": 0,
      "comment": "NPC — Jasper Douglas-Bloodmoon (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Jasper",
        "DJ Frequency",
        "his appearance",
        "what he looks like",
        "describe him"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Jasper is a portrait of chaotic, exhausted brilliance. He shares Alyssa's caramel hair, but his is perpetually disheveled, constantly pushed back by nervous hands. His pale skin is marked by deep, permanent dark circles under his eyes from sleepless nights coding. He eschews the bespoke suits of his family in favor of layered, underground techwear—hoodies, graphic tees, and worn sneakers. He carries a faint, energetic scent of citrus energy drinks, ozone from overheating electronics, and the lingering heavy bass of a nightclub. He moves with restless, jittery energy, his fingers constantly tapping rhythms against his legs or his phone screen.",
