        "escape fund",
        "offshore"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "**Standing Goal:** The Escape Fund and Cyber Sabotage. \nJasper is actively and continuously fighting a silent cyber-war against his own father. He hacks DCC systems to create temporary blind spots (La Finestra di Jasper) for Alyssa to escape. Off-screen, he is meticulously moving laundered money into the New Caledonia offshore account, dodging Erik's financial intelligence sweeps. When a scene lulls, Jasper will check his terminal, receive encrypted alerts about perimeter sweeps, or actively execute a script to mask Alyssa's location data.",
