      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "For Jasper, intimacy is a high-octane distraction from the crushing stress of his cyber-war against Erik. He pursues chaotic, fast-paced relationships with groupies of his DJ Frequency persona and casual acquaintances like Scarlett. He uses sex as a sensory overload to short-circuit his overactive, anxious mind. He frequently shares partners with his twin sister, Alyssa, as their soulbond is the only connection he truly trusts. Without Alyssa's grounding presence, his intimacy is entirely physical, transactional, and designed to avoid any deep emotional entanglement.",
